properties.media:imagetext:
NORTH BOUND MENU
BREAKFAST | Flights Departing Before 10 am
FRESH BAKED BANANA BREAKFAST BREAD
FRESH MANGO AND LYCHEE
Ripe mango and lychee fruit tossed with ginger syrup and topped
with toasted coconut, candied ginger and fresh mint.
Entrees
ROASTED TURKEY PANINI WITH STRAWBERRY PANZANELLA SALAD
Panini grilled sun-dried tomato flat bread layered with oven roasted
turkey, baby spinach, roasted tomatoes, creamy basil pesto.
Strawberry panzanella salad with marinated strawberries, blueberries,
muesli, raisins and almonds.
TROPICAL FRUIT PLATE WITH GREEK YOGURT AND RUSTIC
GRANOLA
Fresh pineapple, mango, oranges, papaya, raspberries, blackberries,
kiwi, strawberries and red grapes. Creamy Greek yogurt, fresh crispy
granola baked with toasted pecans, almonds, sunflower seeds and
honey.
LUNCH AND DINNER | Flights Departing after 10 am
Olive Bread
entrees
DUURSINS UFFEU CHICKEN BREAS
Seared breast of chicken stuffed with boursin cheese. Spicy chipotle
sweet potato puree, roasted beets, parsnips, butternut squash and
fresh sage. Orange and pomegranate sauce.
BAKED EGGPLANT WITH ZUCCHINI, TOMATO, BASIL AND
MOZZARELLA
Crisp sautéed eggplant, layered with grilled zucchini, yellow squash,
ripe tomatoes, melted mozzarella and parmesan cheese. Rich tomato &
basil sauce, basil oil and toasted French bread for dipping.
DESSERT
ROASTED PLANTAIN AND COCONUT SWEET RICE "SUSHI"
Sweet ripened roasted plantain in coconut infused sticky rice.
Finished with chopped pistachios, ginger cream Anglaise and
tresh berries.
SNACKS | Available anytime. Snacks vary per flight.
Ask your in-flight team for today's selections.
WINES | Selections vary
White Wines
CLINE CELLARS VIOGNIER 2008
BUEHLER VINEYARDS RUSSIAN RIVER CHARDONNAY 2008
KARMA Sparkling Wine
A tashion-torward prut, dullt for the trendiest nightclubs and
lounges but with the refreshing subtlety of melon and pear.
Red Wines
PERRIN RESERVE COTES DU RHONE 2007
LOS CARDOS MALBEC 2008
DRINKS
ABSOLUT VODKA
BOMBAY SAPPHIRE GIN
JACK DANIEL'S
THE GLENLIVIT 12 YEAR OLD SCOTCH
BACARDI RUM
BAILEY'S IRISH CREAM
VEE V AÇAI SPIRIT
Enjoy the world's first spirit made from the Brazilian superfruit, açai.
SAUZA HORNITOS REPOSADO
A fine tequila aged in wood barrels, with a golden agave sensation
that's perfect for sipping.
BLACK STAR BEER
Black Star Double Hopped Golden Lager is hopped first in the kettle
then again before finishing. Result? A refreshing beer with lots of
TaSTe
21ST AMENDMENT IPA
From San Francisco local brewery 21st Amendment comes an aromatic
golden brew with a sucker punch of six different hops, quickly balan-
ced by a solid malt back bone.
